- cs.SI (Signal Processing): The paper proposes a method for processing multichannel signals, which is a core topic in signal processing. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper mentions the use of a deep speech model for speech enhancement, which is a machine learning technique. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes an algorithm for multichannel source separation, which can be seen as a control problem in systems engineering. 
- cs.SDSP (Speech and Audio Processing): The paper deals with source separation and speech enhancement, which are subfields of speech and audio processing.
